title: The Driving Test Challenge + Country Songs That Got Us Through A Tough Time + We Geek Out On Clint Black In-Studio
itunes:title: The Driving Test Challenge + Country Songs That Got Us Through A Tough Time + We Geek Out On Clint Black In-Studio
description:
We all take a written driver’s test and the loser has to wash the other five show member’s feet. Bobby, Amy and Eddie share country songs that got them through a rough time. Plus, Clint Black stops by and makes us all laugh!
